Batch Size - 8 (both valid and in train)
No of Training Images - 900 
No of Validation Images - 200 


GPU - Nvidia tesla p100, 16 Gb ( Virtual RAM )
CUDA - 10.0 version
Framework - Pytorch 

Optimiser- Adam 
Initial Learing Rate - 2e-4 
Learning Rate Schedular - divide by a factor of 2 when for 10 epochs valid CE loss is less than best valid CE loss.  
Earlystopping -> Patience = 20 ( Stop training... when for 20 epochs valid CE loss is less than best valid CE loss)

Input_size = (256,256,3)
Mask_size = (256,256)





  





